    <mxCell id="log5" value="&lt;font color=&quot;#e94560&quot;&gt;10:15:00&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#8892b0&quot;&gt; [action] MTO — Sync started for MTO&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
